@Lab14_HostAddress = http://localhost:5014

### Root info
GET {{Lab14_HostAddress}}/
Accept: application/json

### No policy endpoint (no CORS headers expected)
GET {{Lab14_HostAddress}}/api/cors/no-policy
Origin: http://localhost:5500
Accept: application/json

### FrontendReadOnly - allowed origin and GET
GET {{Lab14_HostAddress}}/api/cors/frontend-read
Origin: http://localhost:5500
X-Client-Version: 1.0
Accept: application/json

### FrontendReadOnly - disallowed origin
GET {{Lab14_HostAddress}}/api/cors/frontend-read
Origin: http://evil.example.com
X-Client-Version: 1.0
Accept: application/json

### TrustedSpa - allowed only for 5173 origin
GET {{Lab14_HostAddress}}/api/cors/trusted
Origin: http://localhost:5173
Accept: application/json

### AnyOriginGet - any origin is allowed
GET {{Lab14_HostAddress}}/api/cors/open
Origin: http://random-client.local
Accept: application/json
